videos.headline: Akron RB Ball puts Zips on the board
videos.description: Warren Ball takes the handoff and wrestles through three defenders for a 12-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Zips' defensive touchdown gives them big lead
videos.description: Zips' LB Ulysees Gilbert lll intercepts a pass and puts on the jets to score a 30-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Akron is dominating Arkansas State
videos.description: Zips' RB Ball scores on an 8-yard touchdown giving his team a 31-0 lead.
